#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/autoinst-cdrom.adoc:3
msgid ""
"One option to prepare such a removable medium is to use Cobbler.  For "
"information about using Cobbler to prepare an ISO image, see xref:client-"
"configuration:autoinst-cdrom.adoc#build-iso-with-cobbler[Build an ISO Image "
"With Cobbler]."
