#: modules/client-configuration/pages/autoinst-cdrom.adoc:5
msgid ""
"For {suse} systems, prepare an ISO image using KIWI.  For information, see "
"xref:client-configuration:autoinst-cdrom.adoc#build-iso-with-kiwi[Build a "
"SUSE ISO Image With KIWI]."
