#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-proxy-cli.adoc:12
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/registration-cli.adoc:42
msgid "Restart the [systemitem]``salt-minion`` service:"
msgstr "다음과 같이 [systemitem]``salt-minion`` 서비스를 재시작합니다."

#. type: delimited block -
