msgstr ""
"CD-ROM을 사용하여 클라이언트를 프로비저닝하는 방법은 xref:client-"
"configuration:autoinst-cdrom.adoc[]를 참조하십시오."

#. type: Title =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-major.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
