#, no-wrap
msgid "<SYSTEM>"
msgstr "<시스템>"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:59
msgid ""
"For this example we will use the group we created to select all of the "
"systems from that group:"
msgstr "이 예에서는 해당 그룹에서 모든 시스템을 선택하기 위해 생성한 그룹을 사용합니다."

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "group:mpm-target-sles15sp3\n"
msgstr "group:mpm-target-sles15sp3\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:61
#, no-wrap
msgid "<BASE_CHANNEL_LABEL>"
msgstr "<BASE_CHANNEL_LABEL>"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:62
msgid ""
"This is the label for the target base channel.  In this case, the system is "
"being upgraded to SLES 15 SP3, and the label is [literal]``sle-product-"
"sles15-sp3-pool-x86_64``."
msgstr ""
"대상 기본 채널의 레이블입니다. 이 경우 시스템은 SLES 15 SP3로 업그레이드되고 레이블은 [literal]``sle-product-"
"sles15-sp3-pool-x86_64``입니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:63
msgid "To see a list of all base channels currently mirrored, run:"
msgstr "현재 미러링되는 모든 기본 채널 목록을 보려면 다음을 실행:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "spacecmd softwarechannel_listbasechannels.\n"
msgstr "spacecmd softwarechannel_listbasechannels.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:65
msgid ""
"Keep in mind you cannot upgrade to a channel unless it is an available "
"target for your current base channel."
msgstr "현재 기본 채널에 대해 사용할 수 있는 대상이 아닌 경우 채널로 업그레이드할 수 없음에 유의하십시오."

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "<MIGRATION_TARGET>"
msgstr "<MIGRATION_TARGET>"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:67
msgid ""
"To identify this value for systems in the group [literal]``group:mpm-target-"
"sles15sp3``, run:"
msgstr "[literal]``group:mpm-target-sles15sp3`` 그룹의 시스템에 대해 이 값을 식별하려면 다음을 실행:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:69
msgid ""
"The [literal]``MIGRATION_TARGET`` parameter must be passed in the following "
"format:"
msgstr "[literal]``MIGRATION_TARGET`` 매개 변수가 전달되어야 하는 형식:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "[190,203,195,1242]\n"
msgstr "[190,203,195,1242]\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:71
#, no-wrap
msgid "Options"
msgstr "옵션"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:72
msgid "-s START_TIME"
msgstr "-s START_TIME"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:73
msgid ""
"-d pass this flag, if you want to do a dry run (it is recommended to run a "
"dry run before the actual migration)"
msgstr "-d 시험 실행을 수행하려면 경우 이 플래그를 전달합니다(실제 마이그레이션을 수행하기 전 시험 실행을 실행하는 것이 권장됨)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:74
msgid ""
"-c CHILD_CHANNELS (comma-separated child channels labels (with no spaces))"
msgstr "-c CHILD_CHANNELS(쉼표로 구분된 하위 채널 레이블(공백 없음))"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/client-upgrades-product-migration.adoc:75
msgid ""
