#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rocky.adoc:20
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-sleses.adoc:31
msgid ""
"If you are using modular channels, you must enable the Python 3.6 module "
"stream on the client.  If you do not provide Python 3.6, the installation of "
"the [package]``spacecmd`` package will fail."
msgstr ""
"모듈형 채널을 사용하는 경우 클라이언트에서 Python 3.6 모듈 스트림을 활성화해"
