"cp /etc/pki/rhui/product/content.crt /<example>/entitlement/\n"
"cp /etc/pki/rhui/key.pem /<example>/entitlement/\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:32
msgid ""
"Copy the {redhat} CA Certificate file from the client system, to the same "
"location as the entitlement certificate and key:"
msgstr ""
"다음과 같이 클라이언트 시스템에서 자격 인증서 및 키와 동일한 위치로 {redhat} "
"CA 인증서 파일을 복사합니다."

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "cp /etc/pki/rhui/cdn.redhat.com-chain.crt /<example>/entitlement\n"
msgstr "cp /etc/pki/rhui/cdn.redhat.com-chain.crt /<example>/entitlement\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:36
msgid "Upload the converted certifcate to /<example>/entitlement"
msgstr "변환된 인증서를 /<example>/entitlement에 업로드합니다."

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-rh-rhui.adoc:38
#, no-wrap
